# - Try to find Rdf
# Once done this will define
#
#  RDF_FOUND - system has Rdf
#  RDF_INCLUDE_DIRS - the Rdf include directory
#  RDF_LIBRARIES - Link these to use Rdf
#  RDF_DEFINITIONS - Compiler switches required for using Rdf
